name: Nendoroid – Jujutsu Kaisen – Satoru Gojo 0 Version
description: From the anime movie “Jujutsu Kaisen 0” comes a Nendoroid of Satoru Gojo! He comes with three face plates including a standard expression, a concentrating expression and a smiling expression. Front hair parts with his hair down are included so you can display him with his blindfold off as well!

name: Nendoroid – Jujutsu Kaisen Suguru Geto
description: From the anime series “Jujutsu Kaisen Hidden Inventory / Premature Death” comes a Nendoroid of Suguru Geto from when he attended Tokyo Jujutsu High School!

name: Nendoroid – Jujutsu Kaisen Choso edition
description: From the anime series “Jujutsu Kaisen” comes a Nendoroid of big brother Choso!

name: Nendoroid – Jujutsu Kaisen Toji Fushiguro
description: From “Jujutsu Kaisen Hidden Inventory / Premature Death” comes a Nendoroid of Toji Fushiguro, the physically gifted man bound by a Heavenly Restriction.

name: Nendoroid – Jujutsu Kaisen Sukuna edition
description: From the anime series “Jujutsu Kaisen” comes a Nendoroid of Sukuna! He comes with three face plates including a standard face, a sneering face and a crazed face.

name: Nendoroid – Jujutsu Kaisen Maki Zenin
description: From the anime series “Jujutsu Kaisen” comes a Nendoroid of Maki Zen’in! She comes with three face plates including a standard expression, a combat expression and a sullen expression.
